### Employee Role Endpoints

### Get all employee roles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-roles
Accept: application/json

### Get employee role by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-roles/9351aa22-3cd2-42c9-a07e-e293344908c3
Accept: application/json

### Create new employee role
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employee-roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "IT Specialist",
  "department": "IT Department",
  "description": "Maintains software applications and devices"
}

### Update employee role
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/employee-roles/3d5423c0-ea7a-450c-a2cd-f3e7eab9c281
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Senior Fullstack Developer",
  "department": "IT Department",
  "description": "Maintains company's applications"
}

### Delete employee role
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/employee-roles/3d5423c0-ea7a-450c-a2cd-f3e7eab9c281

### Get all employees for specific role
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-roles/cd2a1f75-84aa-4211-829e-b7444ed522d8/employees
Accept: application/json

